p: Zenith: \bYou look comfy. I told you that you would enjoy your stay.
\bI'm disappointed you had to hear all of that.
\bI'm sure you've figured out my ability.
\bMind control is such an ugly term... I prefer "mind optimization".
\bAnd plus- it's not perfect. I need someone's DNA to do it.
\b...and now I have yours. Funny how that works, isn't it?
\bIn fact, I have the DNA of almost everyone in the region, thanks to the vaccine.
